      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CABAO NICKEL (8) found some support last start but struggled into fourth (20.16), beaten 6 lengths. Was in the money the start prior. Has good speed and can quickly clear the pack out wide. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. GOLDEN GANGSTER (7) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fifth (20.22) in a Special conditions race at this track. Form at the trip sound including 11 wins. Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. Has ability and is one of the better chances. LET'S GO PIES (2) was in the minors two back (20.12) at this track but ran below best last time there, finishing 6th. Form here at the trip sound including five wins. Has ability and can measure up. STEEL SKIES (1) should be thereabouts despite an unplaced run here most recently.",
